            <fr:title text="absolute (co)limit">absolute (co)limit</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>
  An <html:strong>absolute (co)limit</html:strong> is a (co)limit that is preserved by any functor whatsoever. 
</html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
